# Same-origin API: calls go to momentum.geol2.com/api/* and a Cloudflare Worker
# (route: momentum.geol2.com/api/*) proxies them to the backend. Keeping the API on
# the same origin avoids the cross-origin request that in-app browsers (KakaoTalk 등)
# block. An empty base makes api.js use relative "/api/..." URLs.
#
# ⚠️ Deploy the Cloudflare Worker/route FIRST. If this ships before the proxy exists,
#    /api calls hit momentum.geol2.com with no backend behind them and 404.
VITE_API_BASE_URL=
